==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cockshut
<hw>Cock"shut`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A kind of net to
catch woodcock.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Nares.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><mcol><col><b>Cockshut time</b></col> <it>or</it>
<col><b>Cockshut light</b></col></mcol>, <cd>evening twilight;
nightfall; -- so called in allusion to the tome at which the cockshut
used to be spread.</cd> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak. B.
Jonson.</au></rj></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cockshy</ent>⟦br⟧
